@dev Unstake existing staked content and refund the total staked amount to the stake owner
@param _stakedContentId The ID of the staked content
nodes.name: unstakeContent
stakeExistingContent

_canCreate

params._denomination: The denomination of the network ion, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
params._networkFractionAmount: The fraction amount of network ion to stake
params._networkIntegerAmount: The integer amount of network ion to stake
params._primordialAmount: The amount of primordial ion to stake
params._profitPercentage: The percentage of profit the stake owner's media will charge
params._stakeOwner: the address that stake the content

create(address,bytes32,uint256,uint256,b.return: the newly created staked content ID

getById(bytes32).details: Return staked content information at a given ID

params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content

getById(bytes32).return: The ID of the content being stakedaddress of the staked content's ownerthe network base ion amount staked for this contentthe primordial ion amount staked for this contentthe primordial weighted multiplier of the staked contentthe profit percentage of the contentstatus of the staked contentthe timestamp when the staked content was created

isActive(bytes32).details: Check whether or not a staked content is active

params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content

setAOContentAddress(address).details: The AO sets AO Content address

setProfitPercentage(bytes32,uint256).details: Set profit percentage on existing staked content	Will throw error if this is a Creative Commons/T(AO) Content

params._profitPercentage: The new value to be set
params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

stakeExistingContent(bytes32,uint256,uin.details: Stake existing content with more ions (this is to increase the price)

params._denomination: The denomination of the network ion, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
params._networkFractionAmount: The fraction amount of network ion to stake
params._networkIntegerAmount: The integer amount of network ion to stake
params._primordialAmount: The amount of primordial ion to stake. (The primordial weighted multiplier has to match the current staked weighted multiplier)
params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred

unstakeContent(bytes32).details: Unstake existing staked content and refund the total staked amount to the stake owner

params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content

unstakePartialContent(bytes32,uint256,ui.details: Unstake existing staked content and refund partial staked amount to the stake owner	Use unstakeContent() to unstake all staked ion amount. unstakePartialContent() can unstake only up to	the mininum required to pay the fileSize

params._denomination: The denomination of the network ion, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
params._networkFractionAmount: The fraction amount of network ion to unstake
params._networkIntegerAmount: The integer amount of network ion to unstake
params._primordialAmount: The amount of primordial ion to unstake
params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content
